<html>
 <head>
  <title></title>
 </head>
 <body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
      <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
       <tbody>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="AN-email-header" src="{[devName:ANemailheader]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="AN-email-header" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;"><h1 style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 37px; color: #007DC3; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;">NEW CONTRACTS AVAILABLE.</h1> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},<br /> <br /> We've published several new contract opportunities that are matching your skills and experience. &nbsp;</p>
          <ul>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Registered Nurse A [instert link]</li>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Registered Nurse B&nbsp;[instert link]</li>
           <li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Registered Nurse C&nbsp;[instert link]</li>
          </ul> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Open the Alliance Connect app and view the Job board or login via you device browser, using the same login details as when you login to the app.&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</p>
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" bgcolor="#007DC3" style="background-color: #007DC3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;"><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au/nursing-jobs/job-search" style="display: inline-block; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">VISIT THE JOB BOARD</a></td>
            </tr>
           </tbody>
          </table> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;"><br /> If you have any questions at all, please do not hesitate to give us a call on&nbsp;<a href="tel:1300034494">1300 034 494</a>. We are looking forward to proceed your application with us!<br /> <br /> Kind regards,&nbsp;<br /> Alliance Nursing</p></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 20px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 35px 0px 10px 0px;"><img alt="Alliance-graphic-line" src="{[devName:Alliancegraphicline]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="Alliance-graphic-line" /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 26px 45px 40px 45px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 22px;color: #374250;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="/* margin: 0 auto; */">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/alliancenursingaustralia"><img alt="fb-blue" src="{[devName:fbblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="fb-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/alliance-nursing-australia"><img alt="in-blue" src="{[devName:inblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="in-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/alliancenursingaustralia/"><img alt="is-blue" src="{[devName:isblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="is-blue" /></a></td>
             <td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnMTM3MLQMFYj52ERo0E00Q"><img alt="yt-blue" src="{[devName:ytblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="yt-blue" /></a></td>
            </tr>
           </tbody>
          </table></td>
        </tr>
       </tbody>
      </table></td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
 </body>
</html>